rected at cluster level, thresholded at P < 0.001 uncorrected),
(b) but not in PD (P > 0.05 corrected at cluster level, thresh-
olded at P < 0.001 uncorrected). (c) Sample [11C]FLB-457
BPND (spherical VOI, radius 6 mm) was extracted from the sta-
tistical peak identiﬁed in the voxel-based analysis (right DLPFC,
